<Defs>

    <ThingDef Name="OCARINA_MantledBeastsMantleBase" ParentName="ApparelBase" Abstract="True">
        <tickerType>Normal</tickerType>
        <uiIconScale>1.4</uiIconScale>
        <thingCategories>
            <li>ArmorHeadgear</li>
        </thingCategories>
        <tradeTags>
            <li>Clothing</li>
            <li>Armor</li>
            <li>OCARINA_ApparelMantle</li>
        </tradeTags>
        <apparel>
            <countsAsClothingForNudity>false</countsAsClothingForNudity>
            <developmentalStageFilter>Child, Adult</developmentalStageFilter>
            <careIfWornByCorpse>false</careIfWornByCorpse>
            <careIfDamaged>false</careIfDamaged>
            <bodyPartGroups>
                <li>UpperHead</li>
            </bodyPartGroups>
            <layers>
                <li>Overhead</li>
            </layers>
            <drawData>
                <dataNorth>
                    <layer>-3</layer>
                </dataNorth>
            </drawData>
            <parentTagDef>ApparelHead</parentTagDef>
        </apparel>
        <modExtensions>
            <li Class="MantledBeasts.DefModExtension_ClothingRestriction">
                <requiredGenesToEquip>
                    <li>OCARINA_MantledBeastsFur</li>
                </requiredGenesToEquip>
            </li>
        </modExtensions>
        <colorGenerator Class="ColorGenerator_StandardApparel" />
    </ThingDef>

    <ThingDef ParentName="OCARINA_MantledBeastsMantleBase">
        <defName>OCARINA_Apparel_ArchotechMantle</defName>
        <label>archotech visor</label>
        <description>A wearable visor made specifically for the Va'ji (other xenotypes cannot wear these visors), this is a piece of archotechnology created by an archotech that shows favor towards the Va'ji. This archotech visor is incredibly powerful, capable of boosting a Va'ji's abilities nearly tenfold. \n\nVisors are important parts of Va'ji society, much like clothing is to other xenotypes. Va'ji prefer to wear their visors for most of their lives, as they function not only as fashion and individual expression, but as utility to help improve their poor eyesight and improve communication.</description>
        <techLevel>Ultra</techLevel>
        <thingClass>MantledBeasts.Apparel_MoodTexture</thingClass>
        <smeltable>false</smeltable>
        <graphicData>
            <texPath>Things/Pawn/Humanlike/Apparel/ArchotechMantle/ArchotechMantle</texPath>
            <graphicClass>Graphic_Single</graphicClass>
        </graphicData>
        <statBases>
            <MarketValue>4200</MarketValue>
            <MaxHitPoints>400</MaxHitPoints>
            <Mass>0.24</Mass>
            <ArmorRating_Sharp>1.30</ArmorRating_Sharp>
            <ArmorRating_Blunt>0.76</ArmorRating_Blunt>
            <ArmorRating_Heat>0.70</ArmorRating_Heat>
            <Insulation_Cold>2.2</Insulation_Cold>
            <EquipDelay>1.21</EquipDelay>
        </statBases>
        <equippedStatOffsets>
            <GlobalLearningFactor>0.50</GlobalLearningFactor>
            <WorkSpeedGlobal>0.52</WorkSpeedGlobal>
            <GeneralLaborSpeed>0.52</GeneralLaborSpeed>
            <SocialImpact>0.62</SocialImpact>
            <PainShockThreshold>0.52</PainShockThreshold>
            <MeleeCooldownFactor>0.5</MeleeCooldownFactor>
            <MeleeHitChance>0.58</MeleeHitChance>
            <ArrestSuccessChance>0.52</ArrestSuccessChance>
            <ShootingAccuracyFactor_Touch>0.58</ShootingAccuracyFactor_Touch>
            <ShootingAccuracyFactor_Short>0.54</ShootingAccuracyFactor_Short>
            <ShootingAccuracyFactor_Medium>0.50</ShootingAccuracyFactor_Medium>
            <ShootingAccuracyFactor_Long>0.46</ShootingAccuracyFactor_Long>
            <RangedCooldownFactor>0.5</RangedCooldownFactor>
            <PsychicSensitivity>0.42</PsychicSensitivity>
        </equippedStatOffsets>
        <apparel>
            <wornGraphicPath>Things/Pawn/Humanlike/Apparel/ArchotechMantle/ArchotechMantle</wornGraphicPath>
            <tags>
                <li>OCARINA_ApparelMantleArchotech</li>
            </tags>
        </apparel>
        <tradeTags Inherit="false">
            <li>Artifact</li>
        </tradeTags>
        <comps>
            <li Class="VEF.Apparels.CompProperties_ApparelHediffs">
                <hediffDefnames>
                    <li>OCARINA_ArchotechMantleHediff</li>
                </hediffDefnames>
            </li>
        </comps>
        <thingSetMakerTags>
            <li>RewardStandardHighFreq</li>
        </thingSetMakerTags>
    </ThingDef>

    <ThingDef ParentName="OCARINA_MantledBeastsMantleBase">
        <defName>OCARINA_Apparel_AegisciteMantle</defName>
        <label>aegiscite visor</label>
        <description>A wearable visor made specifically for the Va'ji (other xenotypes cannot wear these visors), the aegiscite visor is common among inhabitants of Aegis, with them being rarer as one strays further from known sources of aegiscite. This is the highest tier of visor that can be crafted.\n\nVisors are important parts of Va'ji society, much like clothing is to other xenotypes. Va'ji prefer to wear their visors for most of their lives, as they function not only as fashion and individual expression, but as utility to help improve their poor eyesight and improve communication.</description>
        <techLevel>Ultra</techLevel>
        <thingClass>MantledBeasts.Apparel_MoodTexture</thingClass>
        <graphicData>
            <texPath>Things/Pawn/Humanlike/Apparel/AegisciteMantle/AegisciteMantle</texPath>
            <graphicClass>Graphic_Single</graphicClass>
        </graphicData>
        <statBases>
            <WorkToMake>8000</WorkToMake>
            <MaxHitPoints>240</MaxHitPoints>
            <Mass>0.18</Mass>
            <ArmorRating_Sharp>1.00</ArmorRating_Sharp>
            <ArmorRating_Blunt>0.46</ArmorRating_Blunt>
            <ArmorRating_Heat>0.40</ArmorRating_Heat>
            <Insulation_Cold>1.2</Insulation_Cold>
            <EquipDelay>1.5</EquipDelay>
        </statBases>
        <equippedStatOffsets>
            <GlobalLearningFactor>0.20</GlobalLearningFactor>
            <WorkSpeedGlobal>0.22</WorkSpeedGlobal>
            <GeneralLaborSpeed>0.22</GeneralLaborSpeed>
            <SocialImpact>0.32</SocialImpact>
            <PainShockThreshold>0.22</PainShockThreshold>
            <MeleeCooldownFactor>0.2</MeleeCooldownFactor>
            <MeleeHitChance>0.28</MeleeHitChance>
            <ArrestSuccessChance>0.22</ArrestSuccessChance>
            <ShootingAccuracyFactor_Touch>0.28</ShootingAccuracyFactor_Touch>
            <ShootingAccuracyFactor_Short>0.24</ShootingAccuracyFactor_Short>
            <ShootingAccuracyFactor_Medium>0.20</ShootingAccuracyFactor_Medium>
            <ShootingAccuracyFactor_Long>0.16</ShootingAccuracyFactor_Long>
            <RangedCooldownFactor>0.2</RangedCooldownFactor>
        </equippedStatOffsets>
        <recipeMaker>
            <researchPrerequisite>AdvancedFabrication</researchPrerequisite>
            <recipeUsers>
                <li>FabricationBench</li>
            </recipeUsers>
            <skillRequirements>
                <Crafting>8</Crafting>
            </skillRequirements>
            <workSkill>Crafting</workSkill>
            <displayPriority>999</displayPriority>
            <workSpeedStat>GeneralLaborSpeed</workSpeedStat>
            <effectWorking>Smith</effectWorking>
            <soundWorking>Recipe_Smith</soundWorking>
            <unfinishedThingDef>UnfinishedArmor</unfinishedThingDef>
        </recipeMaker>
        <costList>
            <OCARINA_Aegiscite>45</OCARINA_Aegiscite>
            <ComponentSpacer>2</ComponentSpacer>
            <ComponentIndustrial>1</ComponentIndustrial>
        </costList>
        <apparel>
            <wornGraphicPath>Things/Pawn/Humanlike/Apparel/AegisciteMantle/AegisciteMantle</wornGraphicPath>
            <tags>
                <li>OCARINA_ApparelMantle</li>
            </tags>
        </apparel>
        <comps>
            <li Class="VEF.Apparels.CompProperties_ApparelHediffs">
                <hediffDefnames>
                    <li>OCARINA_AegisciteMantleHediff</li>
                </hediffDefnames>
            </li>
        </comps>

    </ThingDef>

    <ThingDef ParentName="OCARINA_MantledBeastsMantleBase">
        <defName>OCARINA_Apparel_IndustrialMantle</defName>
        <label>industrial visor</label>
        <description>A wearable visor made specifically for the Va'ji (other xenotypes cannot wear these visors), this visor is much more industrial in terms of quality compared to aegiscite visors one may find elsewhere. Still, an improvement to the Va'jis' natural limitations. \n\nVisors are important parts of Va'ji society, much like clothing is to other xenotypes. Va'ji prefer to wear their visors for most of their lives, as they function not only as fashion and individual expression, but as utility to help improve their poor eyesight and improve communication.</description>
        <techLevel>Industrial</techLevel>
        <thingClass>MantledBeasts.Apparel_MoodTexture</thingClass>
